706089f-b.text:
(1)
Nostrand Ave., east side, south of Montgomery Street. In the foreground
are seen the Nostrand Ave., Trolley tracks.
NEG~ 92S2  April 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, more limited. To the right of the small frame house once extended Clove Road or the Old Bedford Road, which extended from New Utrecht
to Williamsburg.
NNS ~.3357  1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
706089f-b.folder: Nostrand Avenue & Montgomery Street, Brooklyn, NY
